Personal Finance Tracker

📌 Project Overview

Personal Finance Tracker is a Python-based desktop application that helps users manage their personal finances by tracking income and expenses, generating reports, and visualizing spending patterns through charts.

This project was developed using Python, SQLite, Tkinter, and Matplotlib.

⸻

🚀 Features

Transaction Management

* Add Income Transactions
* Add Expense Transactions
* Store data permanently using SQLite Database

Reports

* Calculate Total Income
* Calculate Total Expenses
* Calculate Remaining Balance

Analytics

* Category-wise Expense Analysis
* Expense Distribution Visualization

Charts

* Pie Chart for Expense Distribution
* Bar Chart for Expense Categories

GUI

* User-friendly Tkinter Interface
* Add Transactions through GUI
* Automatic Database Integration

