⚙️ Installation

Clone Repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/PersonalFinanceTracker.git

Open Project Folder

cd PersonalFinanceTracker

Install Required Libraries

pip install matplotlib pandas

Run Application

python3 gui.py

